body:
today i was playing a normal draft game and of course, my team hard inted within 10 minutes, no wards anywhere, and bronze 7 gameplay.....

so every time i engaged and my team either inted right away or just flat out recalled, i asked them what the fuck were you doing. and after that game i got a 14 day suspension, and, like any other annoyed players out there, i look at chat logs. and the worst thing i said in the whole game was, &quot;this teemo calling me retarded because he hard inted and i didnt gank before he was 0/3&quot; (keep in mind he was 0/3 within the first 8 minutes of the  game) {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}

I personally think the NA server is very very sensitive compared to a lot of other regions, and frankly they really need to man the fuck up. **im not allowed to type something to the enemy team word for word that someone else said without getting banned  **. it is especially messed up when teamate are saying things far **FAR** worse to you like sending death threats and using racist language and t h e y d o n &#039; t g e t b a n n e d. Get your shit together riot. you are better than this. {{item:3070}}
